2026-05-13T18:26:25.7679137Z 12    <!--
2026-05-13T18:26:25.7679630Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-13T18:26:25.7679960Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-13T18:26:25.7680683Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-13T18:26:25.7681034Z 16        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-13T18:26:25.7681436Z 17        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
